name: o11.1 — Mundanity — rev.03.1
description: The next day. You know that feeling of darkness and self-evaluation at night when all of the problems and worries become so overwhelmingly vivid. It is so fundamental and insuperable at that moment. You are trying to sort it out in your head, to reassemble your perception of reality until your brain shuts down and falls asleep. In the morning, you wake up to realise that it is all not that bad. There is always a way out. It will reveal itself on the next day.
